{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"substring-after","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/substring-after","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>substring-after</code> 関数は、与えられた文字列内で、与えられた部分文字列よりも後にある残りの部分を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">substring-after(<em>haystack</em> ,<em>needle</em> )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"haystack\"><em><code>haystack</code></em></dt>\n <dd>評価される文字列。この文字列の一部が返される。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"needle\"><em><code>needle</code></em></dt>\n <dd>検索する文字列。<em><code>haystack</code></em> 内で最初に見つかった<em><code>needle</code></em> よりも後にあるすべての文字が返される。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>文字列。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":true,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>XPath の例</th>\n   <th>出力</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>substring-after('aa-bb','-')</code></td>\n   <td><code>bb</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>substring-after('aa-bb','a')</code></td>\n   <td><code>a-bb</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>substring-after('aa-bb','b')</code></td>\n   <td><code>b</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>substring-after('aa-bb','q')</code></td>\n   <td>(空文字列)</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"定義元","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-substring-after\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.2</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko での対応","isH3":true,"content":"<p>対応済み。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"substring-after 関数は、与えられた文字列内で、与えられた部分文字列よりも後にある残りの部分を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"substring-after","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"substring-after","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"substring-after","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"substring-after","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/xpath/functions/substring-after","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/xpath/functions/substring-after/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/substring-after","title":"substring-after"}],"pageTitle":"substring-after - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}